 Destructor turned to his horsemen..."There is nothing here let us return.." 
War spoke up.."So sir getting a little friendly with Kit Kat aren't you?"
 Destructor looked up and gave him a swift jab to the stomach.."I was being a 
gentlemen! Now let us report back to her. And remember..you take orders from 
her."
They walked out of the cave and destructor walked up to Kit Kat.."We found no 
signs of life. I am sorry this was not more help to you. Are we yet ready to 
rerturn to the base?"
